	&lt;li&gt;The most appropriate word to fill in the given blank is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Illiterate&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Let&amp;#39;s look at the meaning and examples of the words given in the Options:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

