	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;Ruffian&amp;quot;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;means a violent person or a troublemaker. (हिंसक व्यक्ति या उपद्रवी)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The sentence implies that when the owner stopped paying the workers, many of them became violent or rebellious.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;em&gt;The &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ruffians&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; broke into the store and stole all the goods.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
