	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option 2 - reconnoitre&lt;/strong&gt;: It means to make a military observation of a region. ((किसी क्षेत्र का) सैन्&amp;zwj;य जानकारी के लिए टोह लेना या जाँच पड़ताल करना)

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example&lt;/strong&gt; - &lt;em&gt;The army was sent to &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;reconnoitre&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; the enemy&amp;#39;s position.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option 3 - reformer&lt;/strong&gt;: It means a person who advocates for change and improvement in society. (समाज में सुधार के लिए प्रयत्&amp;zwj;नशील व्&amp;zwj;यक्ति; समाज-सुधारक)
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example&lt;/strong&gt; -&lt;em&gt; The social &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;reformer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; worked towards abolishing child labor.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Option 4 - naughty&lt;/strong&gt;: It means disobedient or mischievous, but not necessarily violent. ((बच्&amp;zwj;चों के विषय में प्रयुक्त) शरारती, नटखट; कहना न मानने वाला, उद्दंड)
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example&lt;/strong&gt; - &lt;em&gt;The &lt;u&gt;&lt;strong&gt;naughty&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/u&gt; children were playing pranks on their teacher.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;Franchise&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;quot;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Among the given options, the word &amp;quot;franchise&amp;quot; can replace the given phrase.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A franchise is a license granted to an individual or group to market a company&amp;#39;s goods or services in a particular territory.&lt;/strong&gt;(&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;विशेष अधिकार)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The franchisee pays a fee to the franchisor for the right to use their business model and brand name.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;Example: They just opened a new fast-food franchise.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, &lt;strong&gt;the correct answer is option 4&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;Branding&amp;quot; refers to the process of creating a distinctive name and image for a product or company.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;quot;Marketing&amp;quot; involves promoting and selling products or services.(&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;विपणन)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;quot;Monopoly&amp;quot; refers to a situation in which a single company or group has control over a particular market or industry.(&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;एकाधिकार)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Option 1&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; i.e.&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;Magnificence&amp;#39;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The word&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;Grandeur&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; typically means the quality of being grand or magnificent. (भव्यता).&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt; The grandeur of the royal palace left all the visitors in awe.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The synonym&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;Magnificence&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; signifies the quality of being impressively beautiful or grand.(अति उत्कृष्टता).&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt; The magnificence of the natural landscapes is truly breathtaking.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Therefore, the &lt;strong&gt;correct answer&lt;/strong&gt; is&lt;strong&gt; &amp;#39;Magnificence&amp;#39;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Liable&amp;#39; &lt;/strong&gt;as per Option 2 is an adjective that means responsible by law or likely to do or to be something.(उत्तरदायी).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Commotion&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; as per Option 3 is a noun that suggests a state of confused and noisy disturbance.(हलचल).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Power&amp;#39; &lt;/strong&gt;as per Option 4 typically refers to the ability to do something or act in a particular way, or the capacity to influence the behavior of others.(शक्ति).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;docs-internal-guid-d04ae34b-7fff-99d4-59e7-e1a07f41aebe&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;border: none; display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; width: 23px; height: 22px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;22&quot; src=&quot;https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/atKwIxseTD8vRnVUC3oGdufIwU5EBz_2UC-92UEVtdPyAGB6prbAzPqN26KeQtY4RGQbInj_lgEwglneUFSzumGRkMOAaDYEiH75HI-PcLJjxKytS0NzQ7314zrpphHdCdZ-fL2D&quot; style=&quot;margin-left: 0px; margin-top: 0px;&quot; width=&quot;23&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, sans-serif; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;Explanation&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 2 i.e. believer.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sceptic&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;refers to a person inclined to question or doubt accepted opinions.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;It would also simply refer to a &lt;strong&gt;doubtful person or non-believer.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;div data-dobid=&quot;dfn&quot;&gt;Let us take a look at what the options mean:&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;div data-dobid=&quot;dfn&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Cryptic:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;having a meaning that is mysterious or obscure.&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;div data-dobid=&quot;dfn&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Believer:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;a&amp;nbsp;person who believes in the truth or existence of something.&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;div data-dobid=&quot;dfn&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Support:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;bear all or part of the weight of; hold up.&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;div data-dobid=&quot;dfn&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Eminent&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;famous and respected within a particular sphere.&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;div data-dobid=&quot;dfn&quot;&gt;​From the above words, it is clear that sceptic&amp;nbsp;is opposite to &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;believer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;,&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;which means &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;to be&amp;nbsp;a kind of supporter or devotee&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt; instead of being a doubter.&lt;/div&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div data-dobid=&quot;dfn&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
Therefore &amp;#39;believer&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;is opposite&amp;nbsp;to the word &amp;#39;sceptic.&amp;#39;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Souvenir&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The correct answer of the given question is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Souvenir&amp;#39;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Souvenir:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;a thing that is kept as a reminder of a person, place, or event&lt;strong&gt; (स्&amp;zwj;मृति चिह्न, निशानी (कोई वस्&amp;zwj;तु जो किसी यात्रा-स्&amp;zwj;थल या छुट्टी या विशेष कार्यक्रम की याद दिलाती रहे).&lt;/strong&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Example: The recording provides a souvenir of a great production.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;​&lt;/em&gt;By reading the above definition we find that the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;Souvenir&amp;#39;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;u&gt;Correct Answer:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Souvenir.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The meaning of the other given as follows:&amp;nbsp;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Biography:&amp;nbsp;an account of someone&amp;#39;s life written by someone else (अन्&amp;zwj;य व्&amp;zwj;यक्ति द्वारा लिखित) किसी व्&amp;zwj;यक्ति का जीवनचरित; जीवनी).​&lt;/strong&gt;

		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Example: Although their individual biographies are different, both are motivated by a similar ambition.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Award:&amp;nbsp;give or order the giving of (something) as an official payment, compensation, or prize to (someone); पुरस्&amp;zwj;कार देना; धनराशि देना.&lt;/strong&gt;
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;Example: He was awarded the Military Cross.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;​&lt;/em&gt;Prize:&amp;nbsp;a thing given as a reward to the winner of a competition or in recognition of an outstanding achievement (पुरस्&amp;zwj;कार, इनाम (खेल प्रतियोगिता, दौड़ आदि सफलता प्राप्त करने पर) में​)&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);  &quot;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;​Example: This is the&amp;nbsp;Britain&amp;#39;s most prestigious prize for contemporary art.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Optional&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Mandatory&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means forcing one&amp;#39;s compliance or participation by or as if by law.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;antonyms&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;of the word&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Mandatory&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; are&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;optional,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;voluntary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;, elective&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;From&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;antonym&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of the given word, we can say that the word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Optional&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; is the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;opposite&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;in&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;meaning&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;Optional&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;means&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;available to be chosen but not obligatory.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Let&amp;#39;s see the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;meaning&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of other given options-&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot; cellpadding=&quot;1&quot; cellspacing=&quot;1&quot; style=&quot;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);&quot;&gt;
	&lt;tbody&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;WORDS&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;MEANING&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Obligatory&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;required by a legal, moral, or another rule; compulsory&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Permanent&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;lasting or intended to last or remain unchanged indefinitely&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
		&lt;tr&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Extraordinary&amp;nbsp;&lt;/td&gt;
			&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;very unusual or remarkable&lt;/td&gt;
		&lt;/tr&gt;
	&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;synonyms&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of the word&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Mandatory&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; are&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;compulsory, forced, obligatory&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;of&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;Mandatory​​&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;in a&lt;/u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&amp;nbsp;sentence&lt;/u&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;em&gt;It is &lt;strong&gt;mandatory&lt;/strong&gt; for blood banks to test all donated blood for the virus&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;Supernatural&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Let&amp;#39;s explore the options:
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Supernatural:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;caused by forces that cannot be explained by science (उन ताकतों के कारण जिन्हें विज्ञान द्वारा समझाया नहीं जा सकता)&lt;/li&gt;
