&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px;  padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Support&lt;/strong&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;to help somebody by saying that you agree with him/her/it, and sometimes giving practical help such as money, help and encouragement that you give to a person or thing (किसी को (सहमति के आधार पर) समर्थन देना या किसी की (धन देकर) सहायता करना, व्यक्ति या वस्&amp;zwj;तु को सहायता और प्रोत्&amp;zwj;साहन).&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advantage&lt;/strong&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;something that may help you to do better than other people, something that helps you or that will bring you a good result (लाभ या फ़ायदे की स्थिति, लाभ, फ़ायदा).&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Leach&lt;/strong&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;(used about chemicals, etc.) to be removed from soil by liquids passing through it, (used about liquids) to remove chemicals, etc. from soil by passing through it&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;(रसायनों आदि के लिए प्रयुक्त) द्रवों की सहायता से मिट्टी से (रसायनों का) अलग होना, (द्रव पदार्थ के लिए प्रयुक्त) मिट्टी में (द्रव को) गुज़ार कर उसमें से रसायनों को बाहर निकालना).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is: &lt;b&gt;Option(4) i.e. Jargon&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle; font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The word &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;JARGON&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; refers to special words or expressions used by a particular profession or group that are difficult for others to understand. (किसी पेशे या समूह द्वारा प्रयोग होने वाले विशेष शब्द या अभिव्यक्तियाँ, जो अन्य लोगों के लिए समझना कठिन होता है)

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt; Medical jargon can be hard to understand for someone who is not a healthcare professional.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Hence, &lt;strong&gt;&amp;quot;JARGON&amp;quot;&lt;/strong&gt; is the correct word that means the same as the given group of words.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Therefore, the correct answer is: &lt;strong&gt;Option(4) i.e. Jargon&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle; font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here are the other options explained along with their Hindi meanings and example sentences:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brigand &lt;/strong&gt;(&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;डाकू&lt;/span&gt;): A member of a gang that ambushes and robs people in forests and mountains.

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt; The brigand was known for his robberies in the hills.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Glossary &lt;/strong&gt;(&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;शब्दावली&lt;/span&gt;): An alphabetical list of terms in a particular domain of knowledge with definitions for those terms.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt; At the end of the textbook, there is a glossary to help you understand the technical terms.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cannibal&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(33, 37, 41);&quot;&gt;आदमखोर&lt;/span&gt;): A person who eats the flesh of other human beings.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example:&lt;/strong&gt; The book tells the story of a sailor who survived an encounter with cannibals.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer&amp;nbsp;is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Kind&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The given word&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;Malevolent&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;means&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);  &quot;&gt;having or showing a wish to do evil to others.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;In option 3, the word&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;Kind&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;means&amp;nbsp;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);  &quot;&gt;having a friendly or generous nature or attitude.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;So,&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;Kind&amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is the correct antonym of the given word.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Let us know the meanings of other given words:
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Well-mannered -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);  &quot;&gt;having or showing good manners; polite.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Positive -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);  &quot;&gt;consisting of or characterized by the presence rather than the absence of distinguishing features.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cruel -&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);  &quot;&gt;wilfully causing pain or suffering to others, or feeling no concern about it.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;Dwelling&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The given word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Abode&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;the place where you live&lt;/strong&gt;. (निवास स्&amp;zwj;थान; घर; आवास)

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Badrinath is considered the &lt;strong&gt;abode&lt;/strong&gt; of Lord Vishnu&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;​Let&amp;#39;s see the&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;meaning&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of other given options:-
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Dwelling&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;means&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;the place where a person lives; a house&lt;/strong&gt;. (निवास-स्&amp;zwj;थान; आवास गृह)
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Come, sleep in my &lt;strong&gt;dwelling&lt;/strong&gt; tonight&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Aboard&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;on or onto a train, ship, aircraft, or bus&lt;/strong&gt;.&amp;nbsp;(रेलगाड़ी, जहाज़, विमान या बस पर सवार)
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;The Captain and crew welcome you &lt;strong&gt;aboard&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Annex&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;to take control of another country or region by force&lt;/strong&gt;. (अन्&amp;zwj;य देश पर बलपूर्वक अधिकार कर लेना)
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;Hitler was determined to &lt;strong&gt;annex&lt;/strong&gt; Austria to Germany&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Habituation&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;means&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;the action or process of becoming habituated&lt;/strong&gt;. (अभ्यस्त होने की क्रिया या प्रक्रिया)
		&lt;ul&gt;
			&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Example:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Habituation&lt;/strong&gt;, by contrast, reduces responsiveness to the familiar&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
			&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
		&lt;/ul&gt;
		&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hence, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;option 1&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex; gap: 6px; align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;synonyms&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;of the word &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Abode&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; are&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;dwelling, shelter, habitation&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The correct answer is &amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;A pretence&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;An eyewash&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot; means a pretence or a deceptive show or display.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;It is often used to describe something that is done to create a false impression or to deceive someone.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The term implies that something is being presented as genuine or legitimate when it is not.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;It can also refer to something that is done for appearance&amp;#39;s sake or to give the illusion of progress or activity.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Therefore, the correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&amp;#39;&lt;strong&gt;Option 2&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;To avoid talking&lt;/strong&gt; is not related to the idiom &amp;quot;an eyewash&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In writing&lt;/strong&gt; does not convey the meaning of the idiom.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A rare event or occurrence&lt;/strong&gt; is not the meaning of the idiom.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The correct answer is:&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Actions speak louder than words.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The idiom &amp;quot;&lt;strong&gt;Example is better than precept&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot; conveys the idea that actions or practical demonstrations are more influential and effective than mere words or advice. (यह विचार कि कार्य या व्यावहारिक प्रदर्शन केवल शब्दों या सलाह से अधिक प्रभावशाली और प्रभावी होते हैं)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;It suggests that leading by example is a more powerful way to teach or influence others than simply preaching or giving instructions.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Example&lt;/strong&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;The teacher often told her students to work hard, but when they saw her dedication to preparing engaging lessons and staying late to help them, they understood that &lt;strong&gt;example is better than precept&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Therefore, the correct answer is &lt;strong&gt;option 1&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;The correct answer is&lt;strong&gt; Option 3) To avoid dealing with a problem.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&amp;quot;Kick the can down the road&amp;quot; is an idiom that means to delay or defer decision-making or problem-solving, essentially avoiding dealing with a problem immediately. समस्या से बचना&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;An example: Instead of addressing the budget shortfall, the government chose to kick the can down the road by borrowing more money.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;This idiom captures the avoidance of immediate action.&amp;nbsp; समस्या से बचना&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Example of usage: Politicians often kick the can down the road to avoid unpopular decisions before an election.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Therefore, the correct answer is- Option 3.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;The correct answer is&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&amp;#39;Essential&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/key-point-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Key Points&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Incumbent&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;means &amp;#39;&amp;nbsp;obligatory incumbent on us to take action&amp;nbsp;(&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);  &quot;&gt;अवलंबी)&amp;#39;.&lt;/span&gt;

	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Ex&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;He defeated the &lt;strong&gt;incumbent &lt;/strong&gt;CM by a large plurality.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Marked option &amp;#39;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;​Essential&lt;/span&gt;&amp;#39; means &amp;#39;completely necessary; that you must have or do (परमावश्&amp;zwj;यक)&amp;#39;.
	&lt;ul&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Ex&lt;/span&gt;:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Education is an essential ingredient in the making of a successful, rewarding life.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ul&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;​&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;It is clear that&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Incumbent&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;Essential&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(32, 33, 36);&quot;&gt;are&amp;nbsp;similar&amp;nbsp;in meaning.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px;  padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px;  padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;Therefore, the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700;&quot;&gt;correct answer&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;is option&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;3.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px;  padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;display: flex;gap: 6px;align-items: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;img height=&quot;26px&quot; src=&quot;//cdn.testbook.com/resources/lms_creative_elements/additional-information-image.png&quot; width=&quot;26px&quot; /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 21px;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;Additional Information&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;Optional:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;that you can choose or not choose (वैकल्पिक).&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;Voluntary:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;mean done or brought about of one&amp;#39;s own will (बिना वेतन के किया गया काम,स्&amp;zwj;वयंसेवी).&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 700; &quot;&gt;Alternate:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;happening or following regularly one after the other (बारी-बारी से रखना).&lt;/li&gt;
